OL,3,CMan avoids jail and still allowed to
OL,4,Cdrive after woman died in crash
OL,6,FA man whose girlfriend died after he
OL,7,Fcrashed into a lamppost while
OL,8,Ftravelling three times the legal limit
OL,9,Fwill avoid jail.
OL,11,FJay Bayliss, 32, was charged with
OL,12,Fcausing death by dangerous driving,
OL,13,Fbut based on medical evidence was
OL,14,Fruled unfit for trial.
OL,16,FIn July 2017, Sophie Brimble, 20, was
OL,17,Fin the car with Bayliss, when he was
OL,18,Finvolved in a race with Neil Brooks,
OL,19,Fand lost control of the car while
OL,20,Fspeeding and crashed into a lamppost
OL,21,Fin Brynmawr.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
