PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776003065
OL,3,CMan avoids jail and still allowed to
OL,4,Cdrive after woman died in crash
OL,6,FHowever, this did not mean he wasn't
OL,7,Fto blame and was "concerned" his
OL,8,Fdriving license was handed back to him.
OL,10,FSpeaking outside court following the
OL,11,Fruling, Sophie's sister, Aimee
OL,12,FCoombes, said as a family they were
OL,13,Fangry with the decision.
OL,15,F"He's basically got away with it. I
OL,16,Fcan't even explain the anger. We will
OL,17,Fdeal with this for the rest of our
OL,18,Flives and for us it's made it much
OL,19,Fharder because we'll never see justice
OL,20,Ffor Sophie."
