PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776003065
OL,3,CMan avoids jail and still allowed to
OL,4,Cdrive after woman died in crash
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Justice (MOJ) said
OL,7,Fthese circumstances are "rare" but
OL,8,Funderstand the distress a case like
OL,9,Fthis can cause.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the MOJ added: "We
OL,12,Fare already working to reform the law
OL,13,Faround unfitness to plead. The Law
OL,14,FCommission is carrying out further
OL,15,Freviews into related areas of law, and
OL,16,Fwill use those findings to make
OL,17,Fchanges so the policy is fit for
OL,18,Fpurpose."
